                Hi, I’m <span class="text-accent font-medium">Jay</span>.<br />
            </h1>

            <h2 class="font-serif text-[clamp(1.25rem,3vw,2.5rem)] sm:text-[clamp(1rem,3vw,3rem)] font-bold text-primary leading-snug tracking-tight">
                 I learn absurdly fast — and sometimes too much at once. 
                <!-- Curious enough to ask, calm enough to listen. -->
                <!-- Curious enough to ask, playful enough to enjoy the answers. 
                <!-- I chase ideas, savor moments, embrace surprises. -->
